Prism Entertainment Corp said ithas entered an acquisition and distribution agreement withTokyo-based Gaga Communications to make and distribute homevideo titles in Japan under the Prism label.    Both companies will provide funding for joint acquisitionsof up to ten mln dlrs.    Gaga is a subsidiary of Nihon Tape Corp, Japan's largestwholesaler of pre-recorded cassettes.    Gaga will manufacture and distribute the videos for theJapanese market. Reuter&#3;